headline: Global Industrial Real Estate Leader Converts Illinois Warehouse into Turnkey Data Center
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE: PLD), the global leader in logistics real estate, today announced it has sold a data center development in its Chicago market to HMC Capital (ASX: HMC). Prologis, in partnership with Skybox Datacenters, is converting one of its warehouses into a high-capacity, turnkey data center with a marketed capacity of 32 megawatts (MW).
